{"tid":795992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳奕迅IG 恭喜港隊引中港罵戰 大陸網民翻牆洗版","createTime":"2018-08-27T12:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T07:38:03.000Z","uid":162324,"like":431,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"bea6d33588413243c6b407f88d7ecb35e2b16e46","tid":795992,"uid":162324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T12:08:32.000Z","msg":"在亞運會中港隊成員屢創佳績，壁球將包辦冠亞軍，馬術盛裝舞步又有金牌，女子混合泳接力亦獲得銀牌，創24年來最佳成績。港隊成績優異，陳奕迅在Instagram上發佈照片恭賀女子泳隊獲得佳績。不過卻引來一班大陸網民不斷留言強調「中國香港」，這些留言導致香港網民不滿，反擊大陸網民指香港獲勝了他們就拉關係說是中國香港，輸了就只是香港，又嘲笑一班大陸網民特意翻牆去IG留言。只要為港隊打氣，都引來一輪中港罵戰，Eason今次真的是躺著也中槍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這次港隊奪銀是因為中國韓國被DQ，補上亞軍位置，當時港隊開心與獲得季軍的新加坡擁抱慶祝，但都被大陸網民指他們應該去安慰中國隊不該表現得如此高興。所以說，玻璃心即使你不碰，它也會碎！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/200806_5df6b30c0804cf7a383dfe7f3d104651.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F200806_5df6b30c0804cf7a383dfe7f3d104651.png&h=8a2dd081&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n節錄部分支那人留言<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/200807_35bc293112b2f062d56a10006e0ff78d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F200807_35bc293112b2f062d56a10006e0ff78d.png&h=675baf71&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/200807_557d52d48d3d1a32e9c2ebf5d3943186.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F200807_557d52d48d3d1a32e9c2ebf5d3943186.png&h=ba16d993&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/200808_557d52d48d3d1a32e9c2ebf5d3943186.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F200808_557d52d48d3d1a32e9c2ebf5d3943186.png&h=629bbc3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/27/200808_7bac80255bf6c05ccaa168d1a6d563ca.png\"